26
00:01:29,950 --> 00:01:31,680
{\an8}"....karena aku kerabat dekatnya..."

27
00:01:31,750 --> 00:01:32,550
{\an8}"...Malaikat Maut."< / i><font color="#0i0000"></font>

28
