29
00:01:36,190 --> 00:01:38,760
{\an8}"...pukul 12:15,..."< / i><font color="#0i0000"></font>

30
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:41,490
<font color="#ff8000"><i>"...pada selasa malam minggu depan,..."< / i><font color="#0i0000"></font></font></i>

31
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:43,360
<font color="#ff8000">"...aku akan berkeliling di New Orleans."</font>

32
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:45,060
<font color="#ff8000">"Dengan kemurah-hatianku yang tidak terbatas,..."</font>

33
00:01:45,130 --> 00:01:47,500
<font color="#ff8000">"...aku akan memberi sedikit saran
