34
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:49,800
<font color="#ff8000">"Inilah sarannya."</font>

35
00:01:49,870 --> 00:01:51,700
<font color="#ff8000">"Aku sangat menyukai musik jazz,..."</font>

36
00:01:51,770 --> 00:01:54,710
<font color="#ff8000">"...dan aku bersumpah
