37
00:01:54,770 --> 00:01:56,870
<font color="#ff8000">"...setiap orang akan diampuni..."</font>

38
00:01:56,910 --> 00:01:59,810
<font color="#ff8000">"...jika memutar musik jazz dirumah..."</font>

39
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:01,240
