42
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:05,780
<font color="#ff8000">...dengan kelakuan gilanya.</font>

43
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:08,750
<font color="#ff8000">Millie, menurutmu memutar <font color="#ff0000">Victrola<font color="#ff8000"> cukup?</font></font></font>

